    VariableLengthTypeHandler, CascadingTypeHandler, QueryableTypeHandler, ReferenceTypeHandler, TypeHandler4
    public class CollectionTypeHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReferenceTypeHandler, CascadingTypeHandler, VariableLengthTypeHandler, QueryableTypeHandler
    TypeHandler for Collections. On the .NET side, usage is restricted to instances of IList.
